00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:07.460 align:middle line:90%
And that was my journey.

00:08:07.460 --> 00:08:08.876 align:middle line:84%
And that's what I
was looking for.

00:08:08.876 --> 00:08:13.600 align:middle line:84%
