through disease and illness.

00:08:43.270 --> 00:08:45.290 align:middle line:84%
That's what I
really connect with.

00:08:45.290 --> 00:08:47.090 align:middle line:90%
And so I followed that path.

00:08:47.090 --> 00:08:51.260 align:middle line:84%
