00:11:51.970 --> 00:11:55.995 align:middle line:90%
is about my son, Joshua.

00:11:55.995 --> 00:11:58.900 align:middle line:90%


00:11:58.900 --> 00:12:02.080 align:middle line:84%
When I was pregnant,
I had an experience

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:04.930 align:middle line:90%
that was pretty amazing.

00:12:04.930 --> 00:12:07.990 align:middle line:84%
I was in labor for
24 and 1/2 hours.

00:12:07.990 --> 00:12:10.990 align:middle line:90%
I was in a lot of pain.

00:12:10.990 --> 00:12:14.200 align:middle line:90%
And I didn't know any better.

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:16.950 align:middle line:90%
I'd never had a baby.

00:12:16.950 --> 00:12:19.090 align:middle line:90%
And it hurt.

00:12:19.090 --> 00:12:27.190 align:middle line:84%
So after he was born, I was
told that three days later I

00:12:27.190 --> 00:12:29.960 align:middle line:90%
should be back to normal.

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:30.760 align:middle line:90%
Well, I wasn't.

00:12:30.760 --> 00:12:34.460 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't walk.

00:12:34.460 --> 00:12:37.240 align:middle line:84%
I walked like an old
person, bent over.

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:39.310 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't straighten my legs.

00:12:39.310 --> 00:12:44.200 align:middle line:84%
So my husband drove
me to the hospital.

00:12:44.200 --> 00:12:45.470 align:middle line:90%
It was scary.

00:12:45.470 --> 00:12:47.750 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know what
was wrong with me.

00:12:47.750 --> 00:12:50.800 align:middle line:84%
I went in for
exploratory surgery.

00:12:50.800 --> 00:12:53.080 align:middle line:84%
It had turned out
that my appendix

00:12:53.080 --> 00:12:54.535 align:middle line:90%
had ruptured and burst.

00:12:54.535 --> 00:12:57.130 align:middle line:90%


00:12:57.130 --> 00:12:59.170 align:middle line:90%
Peritonitis had set in.

00:12:59.170 --> 00:13:04.640 align:middle line:84%
They drained a pint
of fluid from my body.

00:13:04.640 --> 00:13:05.890 align:middle line:90%
I was in medical journals.

00:13:05.890 --> 00:13:08.470 align:middle line:90%


00:13:08.470 --> 00:13:10.670 align:middle line:90%
I nearly died.

00:13:10.670 --> 00:13:12.880 align:middle line:84%
And then the next
time I woke up,

00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:18.700 align:middle line:84%
a nurse was pumping my breasts
to keep the milk flowing.

00:13:18.700 --> 00:13:21.970 align:middle line:84%
And I wanted to ask
her what condition

00:13:21.970 --> 00:13:28.120 align:middle line:84%
I was in, but all that came
out of my mouth was water.

00:13:28.120 --> 00:13:32.830 align:middle line:84%
It's like my brain and my
other brain wasn't working.

00:13:32.830 --> 00:13:35.410 align:middle line:90%
I don't know.

00:13:35.410 --> 00:13:41.710 align:middle line:84%
So I closed my
eyes, and I asked,

00:13:41.710 --> 00:13:48.640 align:middle line:84%
I guess God, or myself,
what would happen if I died.

00:13:48.640 --> 00:13:51.730 align:middle line:90%
Because I knew that I was--

00:13:51.730 --> 00:13:55.690 align:middle line:90%
I knew that I could go.

00:13:55.690 --> 00:13:58.220 align:middle line:90%
I knew that.

00:13:58.220 --> 00:14:00.010 align:middle line:90%
And so I thought of my husband.

00:14:00.010 --> 00:14:02.920 align:middle line:90%
And his name is Spencer.

00:14:02.920 --> 00:14:08.300 align:middle line:84%
And I knew that Spencer would
be OK, that he would be in pain,

00:14:08.300 --> 00:14:12.190 align:middle line:84%
but he would go on with this
life and he would be fine.

00:14:12.190 --> 00:14:19.000 align:middle line:84%
And then-- now keep in mind, my
son was newborn, a week old--

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:26.215 align:middle line:84%
I saw my son in an
oval picture frame.

00:14:26.215 --> 00:14:35.440 align:middle line:84%
And the picture I saw was
him when he was three.

00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:39.240 align:middle line:90%


00:14:39.240 --> 00:14:42.490 align:middle line:90%
Literally, he was three.

00:14:42.490 --> 00:14:45.380 align:middle line:84%
And he said to me,
mommy, don't go.

00:14:45.380 --> 00:14:48.030 align:middle line:90%


00:14:48.030 --> 00:14:52.440 align:middle line:90%
And so I didn't go.

00:14:52.440 --> 00:15:01.010 align:middle line:84%
And so what that did for
me is that I was so sick,

00:15:01.010 --> 00:15:09.370 align:middle line:84%
and in so much pain, that I
learned a couple of things.

00:15:09.370 --> 00:15:13.130 align:middle line:84%
One is that it is
absolutely amazing

00:15:13.130 --> 00:15:18.950 align:middle line:84%
how much pain a human body
can withstand and survive.

00:15:18.950 --> 00:15:24.650 align:middle line:84%
And two, death isn't
something to be feared.

00:15:24.650 --> 00:15:27.730 align:middle line:90%


00:15:27.730 --> 00:15:34.100 align:middle line:90%
So that's what I learned.

00:15:34.100 --> 00:15:36.060 align:middle line:90%
And I'll never forget it.

00:15:36.060 --> 00:15:38.950 align:middle line:90%


00:15:38.950 --> 00:15:39.750 align:middle line:90%
This is Josh.

00:15:39.750 --> 00:15:41.390 align:middle line:90%
This is after my operation.

00:15:41.390 --> 00:15:44.350 align:middle line:90%


00:15:44.350 --> 00:15:47.160 align:middle line:84%
That's after my second
son was born, just after.

00:15:47.160 --> 00:15:50.030 align:middle line:90%


00:15:50.030 --> 00:15:53.311 align:middle line:84%
That's what he looked
like when I saw him.

00:15:53.311 --> 00:15:54.310 align:middle line:90%
He was a little younger.

00:15:54.310 --> 00:15:58.926 align:middle line:90%


00:15:58.926 --> 00:16:07.120 align:middle line:84%
And that's about what
he looks like now,

00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:14.680 align:middle line:84%
except he's got long hippy
hair, like this, which is great.

00:16:14.680 --> 00:16:17.240 align:middle line:90%


00:16:17.240 --> 00:16:19.180 align:middle line:90%
And then--

00:16:19.180 --> 00:16:25.900 align:middle line:84%
I guess the way it affects me
today is I have a joy for life.

00:16:25.900 --> 00:16:32.380 align:middle line:84%
I have an appreciation
for nature and children.

00:16:32.380 --> 00:16:34.800 align:middle line:90%
Any child is a gift.

00:16:34.800 --> 00:16:37.390 align:middle line:90%


00:16:37.390 --> 00:16:38.740 align:middle line:90%
Nature is a gift.

00:16:38.740 --> 00:16:40.720 align:middle line:90%
Being alive is a gift.

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:47.050 align:middle line:84%
And yet, it's OK when
I hear of people dying.

00:16:47.050 --> 00:16:59.130 align:middle line:84%
It's OK that they die, because
it's what's supposed to happen.

00:16:59.130 --> 00:17:02.450 align:middle line:90%
It's part of life.

00:17:02.450 --> 00:17:08.889 align:middle line:84%
So it just helps me be more
centered and more trusting.

00:17:08.889 --> 00:17:11.932 align:middle line:90%


00:17:11.932 --> 00:17:15.380 align:middle line:90%
That's really what it does.

00:17:15.380 --> 00:17:26.780 align:middle line:90%


00:17:26.780 --> 00:17:30.830 align:middle line:84%
I'm from Belgium, and this is
my story how I changed my life.

00:17:30.830 --> 00:17:34.200 align:middle line:90%


00:17:34.200 --> 00:17:38.060 align:middle line:84%
I used to be a very much
career oriented person.

00:17:38.060 --> 00:17:42.830 align:middle line:84%
For 20 years that was the most
important part of my life,

00:17:42.830 --> 00:17:45.650 align:middle line:84%
together with having a
nice house, and a nice car,

00:17:45.650 --> 00:17:48.380 align:middle line:84%
and a good job, and all the
money and all the things

00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:49.760 align:middle line:90%
that come along.

00:17:49.760 --> 00:17:54.870 align:middle line:84%
And I had decided to do what
it took to achieve that.

00:17:54.870 --> 00:18:00.270 align:middle line:84%
So little by little, I
taught myself in many fields.

00:18:00.270 --> 00:18:05.750 align:middle line:84%
I was fortunate to be
prolific in languages.

00:18:05.750 --> 00:18:07.940 align:middle line:84%
And I taught myself
to type and to work

00:18:07.940 --> 00:18:09.380 align:middle line:90%
on a computer and all that.

00:18:09.380 --> 00:18:13.370 align:middle line:84%
So after a few years, I
became a very highly paid

00:18:13.370 --> 00:18:14.540 align:middle line:90%
executive assistant.

00:18:14.540 --> 00:18:16.780 align:middle line:84%
And for a while,
I even enjoyed it.

00:18:16.780 --> 00:18:18.830 align:middle line:84%
But after some
time, I really was

00:18:18.830 --> 00:18:22.070 align:middle line:84%
wondering what the point was,
and why I wasn't feeling happy,

00:18:22.070 --> 00:18:26.120 align:middle line:84%
and why I wasn't
fulfilled, and why I still

00:18:26.120 --> 00:18:30.990 align:middle line:84%
had this feeling of emptiness
and of yearning, really.

00:18:30.990 --> 00:18:36.680 align:middle line:84%
And a few years ago, I started
to feel very weak and very ill.

00:18:36.680 --> 00:18:40.880 align:middle line:84%
And I found out I had
Chronic Fatigue Syndrome.

00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:43.610 align:middle line:84%
And in the beginning I wasn't
too worried, because I thought,

00:18:43.610 --> 00:18:46.280 align:middle line:84%
you know, it will just go
away and I'll get better.

00:18:46.280 --> 00:18:47.330 align:middle line:90%
But it didn't get better.

00:18:47.330 --> 00:18:50.720 align:middle line:84%
And I tried several
therapies, homeopathy

00:18:50.720 --> 00:18:52.940 align:middle line:90%
and other alternative therapies.

00:18:52.940 --> 00:18:54.380 align:middle line:90%
I became a vegetarian.

00:18:54.380 --> 00:18:58.120 align:middle line:84%
But in the end, I found that my
energy level was continuously

00:18:58.120 --> 00:18:58.920 align:middle line:90%
going down.

00:18:58.920 --> 00:19:02.120 align:middle line:84%
And I felt that that was really
leading to the end of my life,

00:19:02.120 --> 00:19:03.590 align:middle line:90%
prematurely.

00:19:03.590 --> 00:19:05.450 align:middle line:90%
And I was really desperate.

00:19:05.450 --> 00:19:10.250 align:middle line:84%
And one day, my homeopath doctor
advised me to try acupuncture.

00:19:10.250 --> 00:19:13.220 align:middle line:84%
And he sent me to a woman
doctor who was really

00:19:13.220 --> 00:19:15.830 align:middle line:90%
applying light therapy.

00:19:15.830 --> 00:19:20.180 align:middle line:84%
And while she checked me out,
as is the regular practice,

00:19:20.180 --> 00:19:22.490 align:middle line:84%
she told me that my
energy was really so

00:19:22.490 --> 00:19:27.050 align:middle line:84%
low she couldn't really even use
the needles for the acupuncture

00:19:27.050 --> 00:19:30.010 align:middle line:84%
therapy, because that
would take away more energy

00:19:30.010 --> 00:19:31.770 align:middle line:90%
than it would give me.

00:19:31.770 --> 00:19:34.150 align:middle line:84%
But little by little, the
light therapy helped me.

00:19:34.150 --> 00:19:39.080 align:middle line:84%
And I began to feel that I
became a little bit stronger

00:19:39.080 --> 00:19:44.110 align:middle line:84%
again, although I had to return
for treatment once a week.

00:19:44.110 --> 00:19:48.390 align:middle line:84%
Slowly, twice a week, three
times a week, once a month.

00:19:48.390 --> 00:19:51.530 align:middle line:84%
And I started wondering
what I did wrong,

00:19:51.530 --> 00:19:54.500 align:middle line:84%
why I had to go and
get this treatment,

00:19:54.500 --> 00:19:58.010 align:middle line:84%
and why I wasn't able to build
up my energy myself and feel

00:19:58.010 --> 00:20:00.530 align:middle line:84%
healthy and energetic
and to enjoy my life.

00:20:00.530 --> 00:20:03.690 align:middle line:90%


00:20:03.690 --> 00:20:06.750 align:middle line:84%
So I talked about
it with her, and she

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:09.430 align:middle line:90%
advised me to try Tai Chi.

00:20:09.430 --> 00:20:11.760 align:middle line:84%
And that was a
revelation for me.

00:20:11.760 --> 00:20:16.550 align:middle line:84%
It showed me that I could
access my own natural energy,

00:20:16.550 --> 00:20:18.090 align:middle line:90%
the cosmic energy.

00:20:18.090 --> 00:20:22.050 align:middle line:84%
And it also gave me this
feeling that I was really alive,

00:20:22.050 --> 00:20:27.180 align:middle line:84%
that this very vibrant life was
inside me, and it was moving,

00:20:27.180 --> 00:20:28.520 align:middle line:90%
and I could experience it.

00:20:28.520 --> 00:20:30.949 align:middle line:84%
And it was a
wonderful experiment.

00:20:30.949 --> 00:20:32.240 align:middle line:90%
And it was a wonderful feeling.

00:20:32.240 --> 00:20:34.550 align:middle line:90%
I was extremely grateful for it.

00:20:34.550 --> 00:20:37.650 align:middle line:84%
After having done Tai
Chi for some time,

00:20:37.650 --> 00:20:42.100 align:middle line:84%
I was introduced to
classes in body work.

00:20:42.100 --> 00:20:44.040 align:middle line:84%
And I started to do
a little bit of that.

00:20:44.040 --> 00:20:46.580 align:middle line:84%
It was related,
somewhat, to Shiatsu,

00:20:46.580 --> 00:20:50.100 align:middle line:84%
but I felt it was a little
bit too physical for me.

00:20:50.100 --> 00:20:53.130 align:middle line:84%
But it still taught
me a few things

00:20:53.130 --> 00:20:54.900 align:middle line:90%
about what happens in the body.

00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:57.000 align:middle line:84%
And so it was still
very interesting.

00:20:57.000 --> 00:21:00.210 align:middle line:84%
But little by little, and
after several teachers,

00:21:00.210 --> 00:21:02.820 align:middle line:84%
I felt that it was
not for me just

00:21:02.820 --> 00:21:04.930 align:middle line:84%
to copy what the other
people were doing.

00:21:04.930 --> 00:21:07.530 align:middle line:84%
And I started to look
for my own thing,

00:21:07.530 --> 00:21:11.020 align:middle line:84%
to find out what
was right for me.

00:21:11.020 --> 00:21:14.460 align:middle line:84%
And I began to feel more
confident that I could really

00:21:14.460 --> 00:21:18.000 align:middle line:84%
do my own meditation, that I
could do my own energy work.

00:21:18.000 --> 00:21:20.580 align:middle line:84%
And little by little,
people came to me

00:21:20.580 --> 00:21:23.080 align:middle line:90%
and asked me to help them.

00:21:23.080 --> 00:21:27.720 align:middle line:84%
And that's how I
started healing.

00:21:27.720 --> 00:21:30.070 align:middle line:84%
It's not a physical
way of healing.

00:21:30.070 --> 00:21:34.320 align:middle line:84%
It's very much working into
the aura around the chakras.

00:21:34.320 --> 00:21:39.000 align:middle line:84%
I use my hands and the way
that I feel in my hands

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:42.240 align:middle line:84%
and in my own body what's
happening for the person

00:21:42.240 --> 00:21:44.220 align:middle line:90%
and what they need.

00:21:44.220 --> 00:21:47.730 align:middle line:84%
So I really want,
now, to pursue this

00:21:47.730 --> 00:21:50.920 align:middle line:90%
and to continue in this field.

00:21:50.920 --> 00:21:54.420 align:middle line:84%
And I really am grateful
for the things that

00:21:54.420 --> 00:21:56.550 align:middle line:84%
happened to me, although
it seemed in the beginning

00:21:56.550 --> 00:22:00.990 align:middle line:84%
that it was going in
a very bad direction.

00:22:00.990 --> 00:22:02.820 align:middle line:84%
Becoming sick and
a whole process

00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:08.010 align:middle line:84%
of changing the focus of my
life to more spiritual matters,

00:22:08.010 --> 00:22:11.040 align:middle line:84%
the first step was
really to work part time.

00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:13.500 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, you
know, that that

00:22:13.500 --> 00:22:16.890 align:middle line:84%
would allow me to
live the balance

00:22:16.890 --> 00:22:21.060 align:middle line:84%
between the spiritual part of
life and the material needs.

00:22:21.060 --> 00:22:23.700 align:middle line:84%
But I feel now that's not
really working, because you

00:22:23.700 --> 00:22:24.960 align:middle line:90%
need to shift all the time.

00:22:24.960 --> 00:22:27.690 align:middle line:90%
And it's really very disturbing.

00:22:27.690 --> 00:22:31.440 align:middle line:84%
And so that was 3
and 1/2 years ago.

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:35.880 align:middle line:84%
And now I recently decided
to stop work altogether

00:22:35.880 --> 00:22:41.100 align:middle line:84%
and to really explore
my own way and how I

00:22:41.100 --> 00:22:43.110 align:middle line:90%
can be of help to other people.

00:22:43.110 --> 00:22:47.050 align:middle line:90%


00:22:47.050 --> 00:22:49.110 align:middle line:84%
I also found out
if you are happy,

00:22:49.110 --> 00:22:52.640 align:middle line:84%
if you're peaceful, if
you're not judgemental,

00:22:52.640 --> 00:22:56.530 align:middle line:84%
this is like a
contagion around you.

00:22:56.530 --> 00:22:58.500 align:middle line:84%
And it's sometimes
really funny to see,

00:22:58.500 --> 00:23:01.290 align:middle line:84%
but very often
it's just a grace.

00:23:01.290 --> 00:23:02.880 align:middle line:90%
And I'm very grateful for that.

00:23:02.880 --> 00:23:05.930 align:middle line:90%
